      "source": null,
      "inline": null,
      "v2Examples": null,
      "availability": null,
      "docs": "The Comparator specifies the set of supported comparison operations. It also provides the\\n mapping information about which comparators are supported for which values. Services that wish\\n to implement entity filters must provide validation functionality to strictly enforce these\\n mappings."
    },
