      "v2Examples": null,
      "availability": null,
      "docs": "The ListComparator determines how to compose statement evaluations for members of a list. For\\n example, if ANY_OF is specified, the ListOperation in which the ListComparator is embedded\\n will return TRUE if any of the values in the list returns true for the ListOperation's child\\n statement."
    },
